detaileddescription.para:
For Interval placements, this is the distance between the start of the line and the first marker. For FirstVertex and LastVertex placements, this is the distance between the marker and the start of the line or the end of the line respectively. briefdescription.para: Renders a marker by offsetting a vertex along the line by a specified distance.

parameterdescription.para: vertex number to begin offset at
distance to offset from vertex. If distance is positive, offset is calculated moving forward along the line. If distance is negative, offset is calculated moving backward along the line's vertices.
